snippet.title: Atari Lynx Longplay [50] Ishido: The Way of the Stones
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Ishido port for the Lynx. It's a board game, thus only one game (even tho it says tournament mode). Played two games with different options, but it's all more or less the same anyway. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
